<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MySQL on Sutra Library</title><link>https://MorningCigarette.github.io/categories/mysql/</link><description>Recent content in MySQL on Sutra Library</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://MorningCigarette.github.io/categories/mysql/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Windows开启远程访问MySQL</title><link>https://MorningCigarette.github.io/p/mysqlorigin/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://MorningCigarette.github.io/p/mysqlorigin/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="进入mysql安装目录-bin-下">进入MySQL安装目录 \bin 下
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/08/20/ujTIHxi1GU29JPz.png"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在目录输入”cmd“然后回车&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="第二步-开启远程访问权限">第二步 &lt;strong>开启远程访问权限&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在步骤一执行成功后的mysql&amp;gt;下，依次输入命令 use mysql、update user set host = &amp;lsquo;%&amp;rsquo; where user = &amp;lsquo;root&amp;rsquo;;、flush privileges; &lt;strong>（分号别漏了）&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">use mysql
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">update user set host = &amp;#39;%&amp;#39; where user = &amp;#39;root&amp;#39;;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flush privileges;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/08/20/my4CzBkaQIX3UxZ.png"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>